{
  "stem": "3475.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My brother was sent to a-- to a business school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he developed in that direction, in businesses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What did I want-- as a young person?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't really remember, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I believe just-- for a better life, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to want-- my, my greatest love was sports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I used to belong to a club called Maccabi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to do gymnastics and group gymnastics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we used to-- as a matter of fact, once a year, they had, like, a, a performance in the circus.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we used to do our gymnastics there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I used to do track and field.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I, I enjoyed it very much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was probably my biggest love, is my-- you know, belonging to Maccabi and being amongst other children my own age-- or young men and women my own age, and doing gymnastics, and doing track and field, and swimming.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I think that, that was probably my brightest side of my life in Europe at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because we were-- we didn't even have a radio, you know, in those days, no less TVs and everything like they have now.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I used to read a lot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I always loved to read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my favorite books were Sir Arthur Conan Doyle, Zane Grey, and basically, everything about Lawrence of Arabia, and all this-- anything that had something to, to do with adventures and, and with-- the Wild West stories, and all kinds of stories like that.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- I, I loved to read.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I used to read almost a book a day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because basically, the-- you know, that was the entertainment in those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
